{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5YOW5Luq_MTE4Nw_0019","text":"看 這新月發光 或是自願無言地照在錯的河","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":18},"semantics":{"themes":["反思","自我懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["新月","錯","河"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,3,2,4,3,2,2,2,2,0,0,2,4,2,4,3,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["hon3","ze5","san1","jyut6","faat3","gwong1","waak6","si6","zi6","jyun6","mou4","jin4","dei6","ziu3","zoi6","co3","dik1","ho4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"看","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"新月","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"發光","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"或是","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"自願","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"無言","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"地照","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"錯","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"河","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以新月發光自比，反思自己是否做錯了，並將錯誤比喻為「錯的河」，帶有自我懷疑。"},"source":{"title":"忘川","artists":["陳僖儀"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1187","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5YOW5Luq_MTE4Nw_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5YOW5Luq_MTE4Nw_0020","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
